### [Purchase API]

# success_all_paypal.json
POST http://127.0.0.1:8337/purchase
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": 2,
  "taxNumber": "IT12345678900",
  "couponCode": "P10",
  "paymentProcessor": "paypal"
}

